StructureDefinition-CareConnect-Medication-1

This Medication Resource is primarily used for the identification and definition of a medication.

Profile Minimum Viable Content (MVC)

This FHIR profile has no mandatory elements.

Examples

  • CareConnect-Medication-1 Example
